metadata.name: Bibu Bag
metadata.description: Mint NFT. Forge your physical pouch. 1 NFT = 1 Physical Bag. The World's 1st unique LED Pouch to shill your NFTs, both in the Metaverse and in the physical World. Bibu Bag is the perfect pouch to stylishly carry your daily essentials. It features a built-in LED Screen and a Mobile App that displays your favorite NFTs and creates your own Personalised Animations. Easily upload any NFTs via the Mobile Application, or convert any GIFs to the Display.
